solution:
由一阶含时微扰论可知，若含时微扰 Hamilton 量 $H^{(1)}$ 在 $t=0$ 时，作用在系统上。系统初态为 $|k\rangle$，相应的本征能量为 $E_{k}$，则在 $t$ 时刻跃迁到能量为 $E_{j}$ 的 $|j\rangle$ 态的概率为 $\left|C_{j}\right|^{2}$，这里

\begin{equation*}
C_{j}=\frac{1}{\mathrm{i} \hbar} \int_{0}^{t}\langle j| H^{(1)}\left(t^{\prime}\right)|k\rangle \exp \left(\mathrm{i} \omega t^{\prime}\right) \mathrm{d} t^{\prime}, \quad \hbar \omega=E_{j}-E_{k} \tag{1}
\end{equation*}

由题意可知，本题中有

$$
H^{(1)}\left(t^{\prime}\right)=e \varepsilon_{0} z \exp \left(-t^{\prime} / \tau\right), \quad t^{\prime}>0
$$

其中电场的方向沿 $z$ 轴。 当 $t \rightarrow \infty$ 时，式（1）变为

$$
C_{j}=\frac{e \varepsilon_{0}}{\mathrm{i} \hbar}\langle j| z|k\rangle \int_{0}^{\infty} \exp \left[\left(\mathrm{i} \omega-\frac{1}{\tau}\right) t^{\prime}\right] \mathrm{d} t^{\prime}
$$

由于其中时间积分为

$$
\int_{0}^{\infty} \exp \left[\left(\mathrm{i} \omega-\frac{1}{\tau}\right) t^{\prime}\right] \mathrm{d} t^{\prime} = \frac{1}{\mathrm{i} \omega-\frac{1}{\tau}}\left[\exp \left(\left(\mathrm{i} \omega-\frac{1}{\tau}\right) t^{\prime}\right)\right]_{0}^{\infty} = -\frac{1}{\mathrm{i} \omega-\frac{1}{\tau}}
$$

所以

\begin{equation*}
C_{j} = \frac{e \varepsilon_{0}}{\hbar(\omega+\mathrm{i} / \tau)}\langle j| z|k\rangle \tag{2}
\end{equation*}

设 $|k\rangle$ 为基态 $u_{100}$，$|j\rangle$ 为 2 p 态 $u_{210}$，则有

$$
\langle j| z|k\rangle = \int_{\text{全空间}} u_{210}^{*} r \cos \theta u_{100} \mathrm{~d} V
$$

将

$$
\left\{\begin{array}{l}
u_{100} = R_{10} Y_{00} = \frac{2}{\sqrt{4 \pi}} \cdot \frac{1}{a_{0}^{3 / 2}} \exp \left(-\frac{r}{a_{0}}\right) \\
u_{210} = R_{21} Y_{10} = \frac{1}{\sqrt{4 \pi}} \cdot \frac{1}{\left(2 a_{0}\right)^{3 / 2}} \frac{r}{a_{0}} \exp \left(-\frac{r}{2 a_{0}}\right) \cos \theta
\end{array}\right.
$$

代入式（2），则可得

\begin{align*}
\langle j| z|k\rangle & = \frac{1}{2^{3 / 2}} \cdot \frac{1}{a_{0}^{4}} \int_{0}^{\infty} r^{4} \exp \left(-\frac{3 r}{2 a_{0}}\right) \mathrm{d} r \int_{0}^{\pi} \cos^{2} \theta \sin \theta \mathrm{~d} \theta \\
& = \frac{4!}{2^{3 / 2}}\left(\frac{2}{3}\right)^{6} a_{0} \tag{3}
\end{align*}

（上面用到公式 $\left.\int_{0}^{\infty} r^{4} \exp (-\beta r) \mathrm{d} r = \frac{4!}{\beta^{5}}\right)$。将式（3）代入式（2）后，最后可计算出跃迁概率为

$$
P = \left|C_{j}\right|^{2} = \frac{2^{15}}{3^{10}} \cdot \frac{a_{0}^{2} e^{2} \varepsilon_{0}^{2}}{\hbar^{2}\left(\omega^{2}+1 / \tau^{2}\right)}
$$

