\end{aligned}
$$

所以有 $\left(\Delta_{\psi} \hat{x}\right)\left(\Delta_{\psi} \hat{p}\right) = \frac{\hbar}{2}$。因此称 $\psi(x)=\sqrt[4]{\frac{\alpha^{2}}{\pi}} \mathrm{e}^{-\alpha^{2} x^{2} / 2}$ 为最小不确定波包。\\

