对于电子，当外加磁场为弱场时，与之相比，旋轨耦合就不能忽略，即为反常 Zeeman 效应. 此时 Hamilton 量为

$$
H = \frac{\boldsymbol{p}^{2}}{2 m_{e}} - \frac{Z e^{2}}{r} + \frac{e B}{2 m_{e} c} \left(l_{z} + 2 S_{z}\right) + \xi(r) \boldsymbol{s} \cdot \boldsymbol{l}
$$

$$
= H_{0} + \frac{e B}{2 m_{e} c} j_{z} + \frac{e B}{2 m_{e} c} S_{z}
$$

式中，$H_{0} \equiv \frac{\boldsymbol{p}^{2}}{2 m_{e}} - \frac{Z e^{2}}{r} + \xi(r) \boldsymbol{s} \cdot \boldsymbol{l}$; $j_{z}=l_{z}+S_{z}$。
设未加磁场时

$$
H_{0} \psi_{n l j m_j} = E_{n l j} \psi_{n l j m_j}, \quad j = l \pm \frac{1}{2}
$$

不考虑最后一项时，$\left(l^{2}, j^{2}, j_{z}\right)$仍为守恒量，此时能量为

$$
E_{n l j} + m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, \quad \omega_{L} = \frac{e B}{2 m_{e} c}
$$

于是，在弱磁场下，最后一项的贡献可考虑为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\omega_{L} S_{z} & = \frac{\hbar \omega_{L}}{2} \langle j m_{j} | \sigma_{z} | j m_{j} \rangle \\
& = \left\{ \begin{array}{lr}
\frac{m_{j}}{2 j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & j = l+\frac{1}{2} \\
-\frac{m_{j}}{2 j + 2} \hbar \omega_{L}, & j = l-\frac{1}{2}
\end{array} \right.
\end{aligned}
$$

能量为

$$
E_{n l j m_{j}} = E_{n l j} + \begin{cases}
\left(1 + \frac{1}{2 j}\right) m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & j=l+\frac{1}{2} \\
\left(1 + \frac{1}{2 j + 2}\right) m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & j=l-\frac{1}{2}
\end{cases}
$$

对 $n=2$，有

$$
\begin{cases}
E_{20 \frac{1}{2} m_{j}} = E_{20 \frac{1}{2}} + 2 m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & m_{j} = \pm \frac{1}{2} \\
E_{21 \frac{3}{2} m_{j}} = E_{21 \frac{3}{2}} + \frac{4}{3} m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & m_{j} = \pm \frac{3}{2}, \pm \frac{1}{2} \\
E_{21 \frac{1}{2} m_{j}} = E_{21 \frac{1}{2}} + \frac{2}{3} m_{j} \hbar \omega_{L}, & m_{j} = \pm \frac{1}{2}
\end{cases}
$$

解法二 $\Delta E_{0}=\hbar \omega_{0}=2 \mu H_{0}, \mu H_{0}=(1 / 2) \hbar \omega_{0}$ 。又假设 $\mu H=\hbar \omega$ ，系统 Hamilton 量为

$$
\begin{gathered}
H=-\boldsymbol{\mu} \cdot \boldsymbol{H}=-\boldsymbol{\sigma} \cdot \boldsymbol{H}=-\mu\left(\begin{array}{cc}
H_{0} & H \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} \\
H \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} & -H_{0}
\end{array}\right)=-\hbar\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0} & \omega \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} \\
\omega \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} & -\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0}
\end{array}\right) \\
\mathrm{i} \hbar \frac{\partial}{\partial t} \psi=H \psi
\end{gathered}
$$

得

$$
\begin{gathered}
\left\{\begin{array}{l}
\mathrm{i} \dot{a}=-\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0} a-\omega \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} b \\
\mathrm{i} \dot{b}=-\omega \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} a+\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0} b
\end{array}\right. \\
a(0)=0, \quad b(0)=1
\end{gathered}
$$

利用Laplace 变换方法，得

$$
\left\{\begin{array}{l}
\mathrm{i} p \bar{a}(p)=-\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0} \bar{a}(p)-\omega \bar{b}\left(p+\mathrm{i} \omega_{0}\right) \\
\mathrm{i} p \bar{b}(p)=-\omega \bar{a}\left(p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0}\right)+\frac{1}{2} \omega_{0} \bar{b}(p)
\end{array}\right.
$$

式中，以 $\bar{f}(p)$ 表示 $f(t)$ 的 Laplace 变换。由上两式解得

$$
\begin{aligned}
\bar{a}(p) & =\frac{\mathrm{i} \omega}{\Omega} \frac{\Omega}{\left(p+\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} / 2\right)^{2}+\Omega^{2}} \\
\bar{b}(p) & =\frac{\mathrm{i} p+\frac{3}{2} \omega_{0}}{\omega} \bar{a}\left(p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0}\right)=\frac{p-\frac{3}{2} \mathrm{i} \omega_{0}}{\left(p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} / 2\right)^{2}+\Omega^{2}} \\
& =\frac{p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} / 2}{\left(p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} / 2\right)^{2}+\Omega^{2}}-\frac{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0}}{\Omega} \frac{\Omega}{\left(p-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} / 2\right)^{2}+\Omega^{2}}
\end{aligned}
$$

式中， $\Omega^{2}=\omega^{2}+\omega_{0}^{2}$ 。得

$$
\begin{aligned}
& a(t)=\mathrm{i} \frac{\omega}{\Omega} \sin \Omega t \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t / 2} \\
& b(t)=\left(\cos \Omega t-\mathrm{i} \frac{\omega_{0}}{\Omega} \sin \Omega t\right) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t / 2}
\end{aligned}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{aligned}
& E(t)=\langle\psi| H|\psi\rangle \\
= & -\hbar\left(a^{*}(t), b^{*}(t)\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{\omega_{0}}{2} & \omega \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} \\
\omega \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega_{0} t} & -\frac{\omega_{0}}{2}
\end{array}\right)\binom{a(t)}{b(t)} \\
= & \frac{1}{2} \hbar \omega_{0}\left[\cos ^{2} \Omega t+\frac{1}{\Omega^{2}}\left(\omega_{0}^{2}+3 \omega^{2}\right) \sin ^{2} \Omega t\right]
\end{aligned}
$$

考虑到以 $t=0$ 时刻 $|-1 / 2\rangle$ 态的能量值为零点，所以应在 $E(t)$ 表达式中减去 $(1 / 2) \hbar \omega_{0}$。又

$$
C=\left\langle+\frac{1}{2}\right| \mu_{x}+i \mu_{y}\left|-\frac{1}{2}\right\rangle=\mu(1,0)\left(\begin{array}{ll}
0 & 2 \\
0 & 0
\end{array}\right)\binom{0}{1}=2 \mu
$$

所以

$$
\Omega^{2}=\omega^{2}+\omega_{0}^{2}=(\mu H / \hbar)^{2}+\omega_{0}^{2}=C^{2} H^{2} / 4 \hbar^{2}+\omega_{0}^{2}
$$

最后得

$$
\begin{aligned}
E(t) &=\frac{1}{2} \hbar \omega_{0}\left(\cos ^{2} \Omega t+\frac{\Omega^{2}+2 \omega^{2}}{\Omega^{2}} \sin ^{2} \Omega t\right)-\frac{1}{2} \hbar \omega_{0} \\
&=\frac{\omega^{2}}{\Omega^{2}} \hbar \omega_{0} \sin ^{2} \Omega t \\
&=\frac{C^{2} H^{2}}{C^{2} H^{2}+4 \hbar^{2} \omega_{0}^{2}} \hbar \omega_{0} \sin ^{2}\left(\sqrt{\omega_{0}^{2}+C^{2} H^{2} / 4 \hbar^{2}} t\right)
\end{aligned}
$$

先尝试对波函数归一化

$$
\begin{aligned}
1 & = \int \psi^{*}(x) \psi(x) \mathrm{d} x = |c|^{2} \int\left[\theta(x+a) \theta(a-x)\left(1-\frac{|x|}{a}\right)\right]^{2} \mathrm{d} x \\
& = |c|^{2} \int_{-a}^{a}\left(1-\frac{|x|}{a}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x = \frac{2 a}{3}|c|^{2}
\end{aligned}
$$

所以

$$
|c|^{2}=\frac{3}{2 a}
$$

然后求 Hamilton 量 $H=-\frac{\hbar^{2}}{2 m} \frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}+g|x|$ 的平均值

$$
\bar{H}=\int \psi^{*} H \psi \mathrm{d} x = -\frac{\hbar^{2}}{2 m} \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \psi^{*}(x) \frac{d^{2}}{d x^{2}} \psi(x) \mathrm{d} x + g \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \psi^{*}(x)|x| \psi(x) \mathrm{d} x
$$

但是

$$
\begin{gathered}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \psi^{*}(x)|x| \psi(x) \mathrm{d} x = |c|^{2}\left[-\int_{-a}^{0} x\left(1+\frac{x}{a}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x + \int_{0}^{a} x\left(1-\frac{x}{a}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x \right] \\
= \frac{a^{2}|c|^{2}}{6} = \frac{a}{4} \\
\frac{d}{d x} \psi(x) = c \delta(x+a) \theta(a-x)\left(1-\frac{|x|}{a}\right)-c \theta(x+a) \delta(x-a)\left(1-\frac{|x|}{a}\right) \\
+ c \theta(x+a) \theta(x-a)\left(-\frac{|x|}{x} \cdot \frac{1}{a}\right) \\
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \psi^{*}(x) \frac{d^{2}}{d x^{2}} \psi(x) \mathrm{d} x = \left.\psi(x) \frac{d}{d x} \psi(x)\right|_{-\infty}^{\infty}-\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\left(\frac{d \psi}{d x}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x
\end{gathered}
$$

$$
\begin{aligned}
& = -\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\left(\frac{d \psi}{d x}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x = -|c|^{2} \int_{-a}^{a}\left(-\frac{|x|}{x a}\right)^{2} \mathrm{d} x \\
& = -\frac{2|c|^{2}}{a} = -\frac{3}{a^{2}}
\end{aligned}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{gathered}
\bar{H} = \frac{3 \hbar^{2}}{2 m a^{2}} + \frac{a}{4} g \\
\frac{\delta \bar{H}}{\delta a} = -\frac{3 \hbar^{2}}{m a^{3}} + \frac{g}{4} = 0
\end{gathered}
$$

